Oh, my God. You're right.

517
00:29:18.200 --> 00:29:19.519
Thank you.

518
00:29:19.720 --> 00:29:21.392
I doubt it will get this far...

519
00:29:21.480 --> 00:29:24.153
but if she turns out
to be easier than I thought...

520
00:29:24.240 --> 00:29:26.037
there's something you need to know.

521
00:29:26.120 --> 00:29:28.350
-I'm not a virgin, Sandy.
-Not technically...

522
00:29:28.440 --> 00:29:30.670
but times have changed
since you were last single.

523
00:29:30.760 --> 00:29:32.034
SANDY: Now listen...

524
00:29:32.800 --> 00:29:35.519
