for the first time...

525
00:29:35.600 --> 00:29:37.795
I like to give her
a little spanking.

526
00:29:38.000 --> 00:29:39.513
-What?
-Nothing violent.

527
00:29:39.600 --> 00:29:42.353
Just tap her real light
on the tush and say:

528
00:29:42.440 --> 00:29:45.432
"Hey, I'm your daddy."

529
00:29:46.160 --> 00:29:47.593
