530
00:29:48.120 --> 00:29:50.509
SANDY: What are you doing?
REUBEN: Blotting the grease.

531
00:29:50.600 --> 00:29:54.115
That's the best part. Don't be shy.
It's just a little tap.

532
00:29:54.200 --> 00:29:55.997
It's like saying,
"Boop, I'm your daddy. "

533
00:29:56.080 --> 00:29:57.115
I'm not gonna tap her.

534
00:29:57.200 --> 00:29:58.758
Brings them right back to childhood.

535
00:29:58.840 --> 00:30:01.559
Trust me, they're putty
in your hands after that.

536
00:30:01.840 --> 00:30:04.354
I'm really excited about this.

537
00:30:04.440 --> 00:30:06.590
I feel like
this could be one of those...

538
00:30:06.680 --> 00:30:09.592
defining moments of my life,
or something, you know?

539
00:30:10.400 --> 00:30:14.075
I actually think it's not gonna
work out, but I'm pulling for you.

540
00:30:15.040 --> 00:30:17.679
Just pray to God
she doesn't go ethnic.

541
00:30:18.080 --> 00:30:20.833
