of places over the past few years.

546
00:30:32.320 --> 00:30:34.117
-Like where?
-Oh, God, where?

547
00:30:34.200 --> 00:30:38.637
Let's see, Austin, lstanbul,
Sri Lanka, Portland...

548
00:30:38.720 --> 00:30:41.075
Costa Rica, Buffalo,
a couple other places.

549
00:30:41.160 --> 00:30:44.277
-Wow. Were you in the Peace Corps?
-No, I just like to move a lot.

550
00:30:44.360 --> 00:30:47.318
I get stir-crazy if I'm stuck
in one place too long, you know?

551
00:30:47.400 --> 00:30:48.753
Yeah, completely.

552
00:30:49.840 --> 00:30:52.513
REUBEN: Remember, you were the one--
POLLY: Oh, my God!

553
00:30:52.600 --> 00:30:54.909
I can't believe you remember that.

554
00:30:55.000 --> 00:30:58.515
Of course! You were the greatest
delegate in Model UN history.

555
00:30:58.600 --> 00:31:01.592
POLLY: I guess I did manage
to pass a few resolutions.

556
00:31:02.960 --> 00:31:06.396
Are you okay? Because you're
sweating pretty profusely.

557
00:31:06.480 --> 00:31:09.597
No, I'm fine. I always react
this way to spicy food.

558
00:31:10.200 --> 00:31:11.269
But I love it.

559
00:31:11.360 --> 00:31:13.476
I can't believe you're not married.

560
00:31:13.840 --> 00:31:15.193
Even when we were kids...

561
00:31:15.280 --> 00:31:17.874
I saw you as the guy
who'd settle down at a young age.

562
00:31:17.960 --> 00:31:19.951
You were always kind of
like an old young guy.

563
00:31:20.040 --> 00:31:21.029
It just hasn't happened.

564
00:31:21.120 --> 00:31:22.109
[Gastric rumbling]

565
00:31:22.200 --> 00:31:24.794
But what about you?
You ever gotten close?

566
00:31:25.000 --> 00:31:29.039
To the whole marriage thing?
Oh, God, no. No way, no. No.

567
00:31:30.120 --> 00:31:33.556
I'm not really big on the whole
long-term commitment thing.

568
00:31:34.520 --> 00:31:36.715
Why, are you coming
out of a bad relationship?

569
00:31:36.800 --> 00:31:39.109
No. I'm coming
out of eight bad relationships.

570
00:31:39.200 --> 00:31:40.235
Eight?

571
00:31:40.320 --> 00:31:43.551
-You sure I can't get you a towel?
-No, I'm good.

572
00:31:43.640 --> 00:31:47.394
But if the right person came along,
things might be different, right?

573
00:31:47.680 --> 00:31:50.592
