578
00:32:02.800 --> 00:32:05.872
MAN: Occupied. I'm going to be here
all night, dude.

579
00:32:09.480 --> 00:32:11.675
-All right, well, this is me.
-Great.

580
00:32:11.760 --> 00:32:13.159
Why don't you come upstairs...

581
00:32:13.240 --> 00:32:15.117
and I'll make you
some coffee or tea.

582
00:32:15.200 --> 00:32:16.315
REUBEN: Great.

583
00:32:16.400 --> 00:32:18.709
POLLY: I just got to find my keys here.

584
00:32:18.800 --> 00:32:20.119
Oh, shoot.

585
00:32:22.000 --> 00:32:23.194
[Gastric rumbling]

586
00:32:23.480 --> 00:32:25.118
POLLY: Right there, I hear them.

587
00:32:28.080 --> 00:32:29.718
Oh, yeah. Okay.

588
00:32:30.880 --> 00:32:32.950
-Wow! This is great, so cosy.
-Thanks.

589
00:32:33.040 --> 00:32:36.476
-Did you just move in?
-No, I've been here four months.

590
00:32:37.120 --> 00:32:38.712
REUBEN: Rat! Rat in the house!

591
00:32:38.800 --> 00:32:42.679
Oh, no. This is Rodolfo.
He's a ferret.

592
00:32:43.040 --> 00:32:45.395
I got him in Sicily
at a flea market years ago.

593
00:32:45.480 --> 00:32:47.675
He's old.
He can't really see anymore.

594
00:32:48.480 --> 00:32:50.914
Cute. You mind
if I use your bathroom?

595
00:32:51.000 --> 00:32:51.989
POLLY: Sure.

596
00:32:52.080 --> 00:32:54.992
That's not the bathroom.
My bathroom's right here.

597
00:32:56.360 --> 00:32:58.271
Okay. Yeah, because I just...

598
00:32:59.200 --> 00:33:02.033
