I'll just be a second.

599
00:33:02.120 --> 00:33:03.633
Okay, take your time.

600
00:33:10.080 --> 00:33:11.593
I don't believe this.

601
00:33:11.680 --> 00:33:12.669
[Farting]

602
00:33:17.560 --> 00:33:19.039
Go away.

603
00:33:19.120 --> 00:33:22.590
[Shooing ferret]

604
00:33:22.680 --> 00:33:23.669
[Farting]

605
